<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>259</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>lì shǐ de zhǎng hé 迦南259</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lì shǐ de zhǎng hé sòng zǒu le zuó tiān
 zǔ xiān de lì shǐ xiě zhe duō shǎo xīn suān
 huí yì wǎng xī liú guò duō shǎo lèi hé hàn
 huàn lái le jīn tiān wǒ men shēn shēn gǎn xiè shén de ēn diǎn
 ràng tiān shàng de bái yún dài gěi tiān nà biān
 zhè lǐ yǒu wǒ men dì xiōng bù biàn de xīn yuàn
 cóng yì guó dào tā xiāng bù pà lù yáo yuǎn
 zhí zhe de jiǎo bù liú xià jiǎo yìn yī chuàn chuàn.</lyrics>
</song>